Poppy
=====

Poppy is a fork of Warp (https://github.com/warpdotdev/warp), an agentic
terminal originally developed and open-sourced by Denver Technologies, Inc.
("Warp Inc.") under the AGPL-3.0 license (most crates) and the MIT license
(the `warpui_core` and `warpui` crates).

This NOTICE file is provided in addition to the upstream LICENSE-AGPL and
LICENSE-MIT, which remain in effect for all code in this repository.

