Third-party dependencies
------------------------

Poppy inherits all upstream third-party dependencies. The full list is
maintained in the workspace `Cargo.toml`/`Cargo.lock`, and license texts for
those dependencies are produced in `target/<profile>/resources/THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.txt`
during a release build.

Notable upstream-acknowledged dependencies include:

  - Tokio (MIT) - https://github.com/tokio-rs/tokio
  - NuShell (MIT) - https://github.com/nushell/nushell
  - Fig Completion Specs (MIT) - https://github.com/withfig/autocomplete
  - Alacritty (Apache-2.0) - https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty
  - Hyper (MIT) - https://github.com/hyperium/hyper
  - FontKit (MIT/Apache-2.0) - https://github.com/servo/font-kit
  - core-foundation-rs (MIT/Apache-2.0) - https://github.com/servo/core-foundation-rs
  - Smol (Apache-2.0/MIT) - https://github.com/smol-rs/smol
